# Recommended settings for working in devcontainers on Windows.
# Will force everything to LF, except Windows batch files that require CRLF.
# Works with Git v2.10 or newer.
# Ref. https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/remote/troubleshooting#_resolving-git-line-ending-issues-in-wsl-resulting-in-many-modified-files
* text=auto eol=lf
*.{cmd,[cC][mM][dD]} text eol=crlf
*.{bat,[bB][aA][tT]} text eol=crlf